description:
When in Rome, do as the Romans do - is a phrase that most new age content creators & Indian tourists haven't heard or care too hoots about. That is why when abroad - we are showing more of that boorish and brazen behaviour .... sometimes for clicks - other times for the sheer joy of it.
If this new trend of gawaar-swag is not stopped soon - the day is not far when Indians will be barred from foreign destinations.
